_sText:
The second version of de_cpl_strike considered by CAL, this version was rejected due to it's industrial theme, with CAL admins stating that there are already too many industrial maps.  Consequently, the map has been released independently here as an alternative for public and competitive style play.

close to midrange combat inside a warehouse facility. This map was under consideration for use by CAL and CPL in their gaming seasons. Original map by n@rby, based on a concept by Frank Nuccio
